# PWA Icons Directory

This directory should contain the following icons for PWA support:

## Required Icons
- icon-72x72.png
- icon-96x96.png
- icon-128x128.png
- icon-144x144.png
- icon-152x152.png
- icon-192x192.png
- icon-384x384.png
- icon-512x512.png

## Optional Action Icons (for notifications)
- call-answer.png
- call-decline.png
- view.png
- dismiss.png

## Icon Requirements
- All icons should be square PNG files
- Use a consistent design with the FaceMortgage brand colors
- Primary color: #2563eb (blue-600)
- Background color: #f9fafb (gray-50)
- Icons should work well as both regular and maskable icons
